# Auditoo uses exactly two local env files (both gitignored — use the *.env.example in each app):
#
#   apps/api/.env   — Hono, OpenAI, Supabase service role, CORS (also used by `npm run db:seed`)
#   apps/web/.env   — Vite (`VITE_*` only; values are exposed to the browser)
#
# Do not put server secrets in `apps/web/.env`. Do not put `VITE_*` in `apps/api/.env` unless you add code that reads it.
#
# Full list and troubleshooting: docs/SETUP.md §2
